name: gj2ascii
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4.1" %}

package:
  name: gj2ascii
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/g/gj2ascii/gj2ascii-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 65c865410aecd6e4698a120b47531171ee4bc89a511c301c770393f4884ffe8e

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  # FXIME: retry when the entry_points issue is resolved.
  # noarch: python
  preserve_egg_dir: True
  script: python -m pip install --no-deps --ignore-installed .
  entry_points:
    - gj2ascii=gj2ascii.cli:main

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - click >=3.0
    - fiona >=1.2
    - numpy >=1.8
    - rasterio >=0.18
    - shapely

test:
  imports:
    - gj2ascii

  commands:
    - gj2ascii --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/geowurster/gj2ascii
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: 'Render GeoJSON as ASCII on the commandline.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
